00:20:35,975 --> 00:20:38,609
We're exercising our minds.

294
00:20:38,645 --> 00:20:40,378
Yeah, I see that.

295
00:20:41,648 --> 00:20:44,049
Sorry. I didn't sleep well.

296
00:20:44,084 --> 00:20:47,852
CARY: Is it the dream again?

297
00:20:47,887 --> 00:20:50,754
I'm in a room that's not a room...

298
00:20:53,059 --> 00:20:56,385
