300
00:21:00,558 --> 00:21:02,624
We just don't know it.

301
00:21:05,195 --> 00:21:06,461
Clozapine.

302
00:21:06,496 --> 00:21:09,667
- Or Effexor in large doses.
- Yeah.

303
00:21:18,475 --> 00:21:23,937
I personally dreamed of a...
very large ice cube,

304
00:21:23,972 --> 00:21:27,823
which, um, you know, I could
kill for, like, a lemonade.

305
00:21:27,858 --> 00:21:29,818
A nice, frosty...

306
00:21:29,853 --> 00:21:32,285
Mine was...

