00:22:17,196 --> 00:22:19,273
the subject, you,

322
00:22:19,308 --> 00:22:21,998
confusing one hallway with another.

323
00:22:22,034 --> 00:22:23,433
I'm not making it up.

324
00:22:23,469 --> 00:22:25,769
Oh, no one said "Making up."

