00:27:09,579 --> 00:27:12,547
(operatic singing)

362
00:27:12,582 --> 00:27:19,553
♪ ♪

363
00:27:19,588 --> 00:27:20,987
Maybe...

364
00:27:22,858 --> 00:27:24,190
Maybe what?

365
00:27:24,226 --> 00:27:26,593
SYD: Well, I was thinking about that door,

366
00:27:26,629 --> 00:27:29,930
and how it's there sometimes
