00:27:33,969 --> 00:27:35,966
like someone wanted to get out.

369
00:27:36,001 --> 00:27:37,470
Except nobody else...

370
00:27:37,505 --> 00:27:40,801
And then I thought, you know
I've had that feeling for weeks

371
00:27:40,836 --> 00:27:44,143
of how sometimes this place
