00:27:56,402 --> 00:27:59,591
And not reality itself.

377
00:27:59,626 --> 00:28:00,826
(sighs)

378
00:28:00,861 --> 00:28:03,462
- SYD: What?
- Just be careful.

379
00:28:05,165 --> 00:28:09,067
- What do you mean?
- Nothing. It's...

380
00:28:09,102 --> 00:28:11,602
Just, with your diagnosis

