00:29:33,574 --> 00:29:35,073
Dr. Busker said it's like how

409
00:29:35,108 --> 00:29:36,707
you're not supposed to wake a sleep walker,

410
00:29:36,742 --> 00:29:38,229
but I mean, I just wanna
make sure that you're not...

